@startuml
title MACPro Appian Connector - Control Flow Sequence Diagram

actor Developer
participant "GitHub Repository" as GitHub
participant "GitHub Actions" as GHA
participant "run Script" as Run
participant "Serverless Framework" as Serverless
participant "AWS CloudFormation" as CF
participant "ECS Task" as ECS
participant "Appian" as Appian
participant "Kafka Connector" as Connector
participant "BigMAC" as BigMAC
participant "SSM Parameter Store" as SSM
participant "Secrets Manager" as Secrets
participant "CloudWatch" as CW
participant "EventBridge" as EB
participant "SNS Topic" as SNS
participant "Security Hub" as SecHub
participant "Jira" as Jira

== Development Phase ==
Developer -> GitHub: Push code changes
activate GitHub
GitHub -> GHA: Trigger CI/CD workflow
activate GHA
GHA -> GHA: Run pre-commit checks
GHA -> GHA: Execute unit tests
GHA -> GHA: Dependency review
GHA -> GHA: Secret detection (detect-secrets)
GHA -> GHA: CloudFormation static analysis (cfn-nag)
deactivate GHA

== Deployment Phase ==
Developer -> Run: Execute ./run deploy
activate Run
Run -> Run: Compile TypeScript
Run -> Run: Manage dependencies
Run -> Serverless: Invoke deployment
activate Serverless
Serverless -> SSM: Fetch configuration parameters
activate SSM
SSM --> Serverless: Return parameters
deactivate SSM
Serverless -> Secrets: Fetch secrets
activate Secrets
Secrets --> Serverless: Return secrets
deactivate Secrets
Serverless -> CF: Deploy infrastructure
activate CF
CF -> ECS: Create/Update ECS tasks
activate ECS
CF -> SNS: Create/Update SNS topic
CF -> EB: Create EventBridge rules
CF --> Serverless: Deployment complete
deactivate CF
deactivate Serverless
deactivate Run

== Runtime Data Streaming Phase ==
ECS -> Appian: Poll for data changes
activate Appian
Appian --> ECS: Return data changes
deactivate Appian
ECS -> Connector: Process data changes
activate Connector
Connector -> Connector: Transform data
Connector -> BigMAC: Stream data to BigMAC
activate BigMAC
BigMAC --> Connector: Acknowledge receipt
deactivate BigMAC
deactivate Connector
ECS -> CW: Send metrics and logs
activate CW
deactivate ECS

== Monitoring and Alerting Phase ==
CW -> EB: Trigger on threshold breach
activate EB
EB -> SNS: Publish alert notification
activate SNS
SNS -> Developer: Send notification (email/Slack)
deactivate SNS
deactivate EB

== Failure Handling Phase ==
ECS -> ECS: Task failure occurs
activate ECS
ECS -> CW: Log failure event
CW -> EB: Trigger failure rule
activate EB
EB -> SNS: Publish failure alert
activate SNS
SNS -> Developer: Send alert notification
deactivate SNS
deactivate EB
deactivate ECS

== Security Monitoring Phase ==
SecHub -> SecHub: Generate security findings
activate SecHub
SecHub -> GHA: Sync findings via workflow
activate GHA
GHA -> Jira: Create/Update Jira issues
activate Jira
Jira --> GHA: Issue created/updated
deactivate Jira
deactivate GHA
deactivate SecHub

== PR Integration Phase ==
Developer -> GitHub: Create Pull Request
activate GitHub
GitHub -> GHA: Trigger PR workflow
activate GHA
GHA -> Jira: Create comment on Jira issue
activate Jira
Jira --> GHA: Comment added
deactivate Jira
deactivate GHA
deactivate GitHub

@enduml
